- But...

317
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:48,224
- We have the same father.
- That's not true!

318
00:43:48,480 --> 00:43:50,198
Valerie, come back!

319
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:54,123
Valerie, my father is Weasel!

320
00:44:37,960 --> 00:44:39,916
I will, I won't...

321
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:43,664
I will, I won't...

322
00:44:44,120 --> 00:44:45,166
I will!

323
