could have saved us both.

333
00:46:00,160 --> 00:46:02,116
She has my blood.

334
00:46:03,960 --> 00:46:06,611
How is that?
Her father was the Bishop.

335
00:46:07,960 --> 00:46:10,178
I was the Bishop!

336
00:46:10,920 --> 00:46:12,968
I'm Valerie's father!

337
00:46:13,400 --> 00:46:14,458
You lie.

338
00:46:15,240 --> 00:46:16,309
A drink...

339
00:46:17,160 --> 00:46:18,479
- A drink...
- No!

340
00:46:19,160 --> 00:46:21,731
First tell me how to prolong my youth.

341
00:46:21,960 --> 00:46:23,780
Save Valerie!

342
00:46:26,880 --> 00:46:29,747
Our salvation lies in her blood.

343
00:46:31,360 --> 00:46:32,622
Valerie.

344
00:46:33,640 --> 00:46:36,017
Cursed Valerie.

345
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:43,578
It's me.

346
00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:47,308
Father!

347
00:46:48,040 --> 00:46:49,553
My child!

348
00:46:53,640 --> 00:46:54,834
Take this.

349
00:47:01,800 --> 00:47:03,836
No, I'm squeamish!

350
00:47:05,360 --> 00:47:09,103
