389
00:51:35,640 --> 00:51:38,632
<i>Weasel is neither your father nor mine.</i>

390
00:51:39,720 --> 00:51:42,041
<i>You have prolonged his life.</i>

391
00:51:43,040 --> 00:51:46,692
<i>I wanted be your protector,
friend, and husband, but it's too late.</i>

392
00:51:47,480 --> 00:51:50,085
<i>Farewell Valerie,
Your Eagle.</i>

393
00:51:51,240 --> 00:51:52,275
Valerie?

394
00:51:52,800 --> 00:51:54,153
Valerie, what happened to you?

395
00:51:54,520 --> 00:51:55,487
Come.

396
00:51:55,720 --> 00:51:56,732
Hedvika.

397
00:52:10,120 --> 00:52:11,189
Hedvika?

398
00:52:12,480 --> 00:52:15,062
Hedvika, what happend to you? Hedvika?

399
00:52:17,360 --> 00:52:19,055
