- Aren't they stained?

409
00:53:00,920 --> 00:53:02,751
You've been eating berries.

410
00:53:10,040 --> 00:53:12,907
I'm not afraid of anything
when you're with me.

411
00:53:14,760 --> 00:53:16,182
I'm so happy.

412
00:53:16,920 --> 00:53:18,820
I've never had a close friend.

413
00:53:46,240 --> 00:53:47,343
Valerie?

414
00:53:48,440 --> 00:53:50,192
Valerie, I'm saved!

415
00:53:51,400 --> 00:53:53,197
- Hedvika.
- See?

416
00:53:53,400 --> 00:53:54,844
The mark is gone.

417
00:54:00,640 --> 00:54:02,790
Your kisses have restored my health.

418
00:54:02,840 --> 00:54:04,171
You're so beautiful.

419
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:10,002
