It's her! The witch!

429
00:54:46,720 --> 00:54:49,188
Don't believe him! I swear he's lying.

430
00:54:49,440 --> 00:54:50,976
Begone, Satan!

431
00:54:52,240 --> 00:54:54,731
Seize her! To the stake with her!

432
00:55:15,120 --> 00:55:17,452
